column2: SELECT TOP # f.specobjid AS id, f.plate, f.mjd, f.fiberid AS fiber, f.ra, f.dec, f.z_noqso AS redshift, f.Z_ERR_NOQSO AS redshifterr, f.CLASS_NOQSO AS class, f.Chabrier_MILES_metallicity_lightW AS MetMilesW, f.Chabrier_MILES_age_massW AS MetMilesM, f.Chabrier_ELODIE_metallicity_lightW AS MetEloW, f.Chabrier_ELODIE_metallicity_massW as MetEloM FROM sdssEbossFirefly f INNER JOIN  (SELECT specobjid AS id, MAX(Chabrier_MILES_metallicity_lightW) AS MetMilesW  FROM sdssEbossFirefly  GROUP BY specobjid) groupedf ON f.specobjid = groupedf.specobjid AND f.f.Chabrier_MILES_metallicity_lightW = groupedf.f.Chabrier_MILES_metallicity_lightW WHERE f.z_noqso > # AND f.Z_ERR_NOQSO < # AND f.CLASS_NOQSO = &&& AND f.Chabrier_MILES_metallicity_lightW != # AND f.Chabrier_ELODIE_metallicity_lightW != #
